{"title":"一个纯粹的人的颂歌——献给焦裕禄同志","authors":["李瑛"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":2,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个纯粹的人的颂歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给焦裕禄同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李瑛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莽莽的黄河哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淘尽了多少秋冬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚的流沙哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淹没了多少繁星；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透过报纸的铅字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个高大的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匆匆行走；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗巨大的心脏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在沙梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砰砰跳动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪闪的盐碛呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑟瑟的蒿蓬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汹涌的流沙呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼啸的涛声；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可曾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可曾认识他是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我该怎样告诉你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉你这"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不朽的姓名？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焦——裕——禄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个金灿灿的大字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一段伟大的人生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们为他雕象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该用什么原料？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——井冈山的石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延河的水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——瑞金的古柏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京的松。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是毛泽东思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指给了他战斗的方向；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是毛泽东思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"校正了他革命的准星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少个风雪的夜晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他用《毛泽东选集》里的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做自己的道路；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他用《毛泽东选集》里的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做自己的标灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，他挺立的脊骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似钢浇铁铸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，他滚沸的热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似岩浆奔腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他骨硬——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就不怕天塌地倾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他心红——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对人民献出了最大的热情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他胸膛里装着的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民，人民，人民；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他思潮里想着的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命，革命，革命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，人生——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮丽的人生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他为我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作了多好的注解："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——多么形象和深刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——多么完整而生动！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党，伟大的党呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你给今天的世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造了多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新鲜的、活跃的、强大的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焦裕禄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我们呼唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沸腾着怎样的激情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不是你么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪洋里高挺前胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为制伏亘古的洪水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你肩负一天雷雨；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不是你么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙窝上踉跄的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为缚住漫野流沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你奔跑了多少路程！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涛吞没的屋脊哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄沙压断的梁栋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人迎风的白发哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿女夜半的呼声……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着这满眼的风沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，比子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射向自己的胸膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要愤怒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着这泛滥的河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，比鲜血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌出自己的伤口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还更疼痛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人民，为祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少日夜——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你扶着一根树枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去探测茫茫水路；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少日夜——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你捏紧一支铅笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去记录千里风情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪管白帐子大雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打湿你张张图纸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你咬一口干粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续战斗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪管天昏地暗的黄沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌满你件件衣领，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你揉一揉眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续追踪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的身影呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"始终是顶天立地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的姿态呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍然是坚定而从容！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里乡亲们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声轻轻地哭笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都撼动着你的心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里乡亲们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一丝飞动的神色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都牵动你的眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不顾骄阳燃烧的沙粒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烫肿你的脚掌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管北风撕卷的大雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冻红你的脖颈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少春夏——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从一块地到一块地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去查看压苗的盐碱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少秋冬——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从一家门到一家门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去问候阶级的弟兄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛他们的炕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连着你的胸口——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸一摸，是热是冷？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛他们的锅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连着你的肠胃——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看一看，是饱是空？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你怀念着兰考的大地："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一粒花生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个棉铃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是否被水沤风撼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你怀念着兰考的大地："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一只豆荚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一棵小麦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是否被碱打沙封。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你多想变做一棵树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去挡住流沙万顷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你多想变做一袋土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去锁住肆疟的蛟龙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你多愿用自己的身体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给他们遮风蔽雨；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你多愿走进每一间草庵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去点亮他们家家的小灯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使在病中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在昏迷里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也听得见那里在落雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使在病中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在睡梦里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也感受到那里在刮风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你担心那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每社每队的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座座畜棚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一眼眼井；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你担心那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每家每户的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一垛垛土墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根根绳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同那里的一草一木"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连得紧紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛它们的根须，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最敏感的神经！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你呀，在病床上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躺不住了，你坐起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要去战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象当年在火线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲锋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要到那碱堆里去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拾起你使用的锨板；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要到沙丘上去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找你的誓语声声！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你呀，在病床上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躺不住了，你坐起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用干瘦的手指，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向战友要一把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兰考的麦粒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着看着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的心早飞回了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾走过的阡陌小径，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾踏遍的牛屋草棚……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战友面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有多少话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要讲呵，讲呵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可在党的面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你生命的最后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却只有一句申请："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待死后把自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋在沙丘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好看着同志们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行斗争……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你至死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"始终怀念着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兰考、中国以及全世界的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一寸沸腾的土地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"始终怀念着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十六万、六亿五千万和三十亿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗的姐妹弟兄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你每一次躺下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便想起他们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是否都有一片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遮霜的瓦？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你每一次端起饭碗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就想起他们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是否都有一根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒烟的烟囱？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的肺叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和非洲黑人的渔帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起呼吸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的心脏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和拉美印第安人的木杵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐跳动……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，焦裕禄呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国大地的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一棵秧苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎不怀念你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五大洲云水间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎不回响着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你坚实的脚步声！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们很多人和你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不相识，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但你的生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却怎样震动了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们每个人的生命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们清晰地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听到你殷切的召唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感到你火炽的感情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那一顶旧布帽底下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"褪色的双肩上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那溅满泥泞的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽起的裤腿上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以看出——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不正是你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风尘仆仆地向我们走来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走来，和我们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈论阶级，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈论革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈论理想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈论人生……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用流沙上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不灭的脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对我们谆谆教诲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用河道里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晶亮的汗点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对我们切切叮咛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和黄继光一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战场上该怎样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲锋陷阵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和张思德一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大自然面前该怎样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用沾泥的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开肩头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小的布袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取出《矛盾论》、《实践论》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和那盐渍浸透的笔记本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对着今日的世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同我们一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"研究，讲解，印证——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不朽的真理；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后又按主席的指示，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带领我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从五千里路的尽头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续起程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你呵，仍然是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开襟解怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帽耳掀动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你呵，仍然是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍着病痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈笑风生……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焦裕禄——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们亲爱的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志、战友和弟兄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你泥土般纯朴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火炭般热情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活得这样骄傲——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺胸走来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首走去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在长长的四十二年里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你没有愧对过自己的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次呼吸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在短短的四十二年里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的生命亮过天河里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最亮的星星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你测量的蓝图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制订的规划，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还挂在县委"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结满盐碱的墙上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但你逢人便讲的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义、共产主义的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不早已挂在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个人的心中！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍巍的昆仑山呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚的扬子江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉沉的大地呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩浩的苍穹："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请记着吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一位"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党员的姓名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请记着吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焦裕禄——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东的好学生！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请把千斤重担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交在我们的肩头吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不怕任何嚣张的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妖魔鬼怪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不惧什么弥天的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴雨狂风！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都决心象他那样——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去认识，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去行动！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看呵，在我们伟大的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"董存瑞爆破的手臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍在高举；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邱少云潜伏的枪口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍在待命；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋开动的汽车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍在疾驰；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦贤得操纵的轮机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍在轰鸣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王进喜和他的伙伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在高速掘进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大庆的油井；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈永贵和他的伙伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在隆隆的传出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨的夯声……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是今天我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代的色彩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是今天我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪的面容！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是这样骄傲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一个个平凡的生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一经毛泽东思想的熔炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就能发出如此巨大的热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让那盐堆碱窝里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油绿的庄稼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我们作证；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让那沙碛滚滚的河道上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高耸的泡桐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我们作证——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党呵，请相信我们吧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地陷，我们敢托！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天塌，我们敢顶！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，我们用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁的誓言和信心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来悼念我们行列中的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一名亲爱的同志、战友和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟兄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们将更紧的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把毛泽东思想红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高擎更高擎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤，在我们手中！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀，在我们手中！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步枪，在我们手中！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界一定会属于我们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利一定会属于我们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听，随着迎面拂来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风阵阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四面八方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不已传来如雪的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和震天撼地的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年二月十三——十四日于北京"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}